n the faith, and increased in number daily.","year":53},{"id":"recxipFQsVXMzs9XY","ref":"Acts.16.6","text":"Now when they had gone throughout Phrygia and the region of Galatia, and were forbidden of the Holy Ghost to preach the word in Asia,","year":53},{"id":"rec4GHUzFBRAzbrx0","ref":"Acts.16.7","text":"After they were come to Mysia, they assayed to go into Bithynia: but the Spirit suffered them not.","year":53},{"id":"recHDvgAdezwabOcq","ref":"Acts.16.8","text":"And they passing by Mysia came down to Troas.","year":53}]}
